From: Wu Zhangjin <zhangjin.wu@windriver.com>
Date: Wed, 21 Jul 2010 10:54:20 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] amcc_kilauea_405ex: kilauea.dts: add gpio support

Add GPIO Support on PPC40x and PPC44x SOCs.

Signed-off-by: Wu Zhangjin <zhangjin.wu@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/kilauea.dts |    5 +++++
 1 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/kilauea.dts b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/kilauea.dts
index 13f1e58..085d01d 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/kilauea.dts
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/kilauea.dts
@@ -271,6 +271,11 @@
 				interrupts = <0x7 0x4>;
 			};
 
+			GPIO0: gpio@ef600800 {
+				compatible = "ibm,ppc4xx-gpio";
+				reg = <0xef600800 0x00000048>;
+			};
+
 			RGMII0: emac-rgmii@ef600b00 {
 				compatible = "ibm,rgmii-405ex", "ibm,rgmii";
 				reg = <0xef600b00 0x00000104>;
